				<div class="hvres-meaning small">• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Tr%C3%A3i/%C4%90%E1%BB%81-B%C3%A3o-Ph%C3%BAc-nham/poem-wyQSAoySlvz4SQ0MXTsaqA">Đề Bão Phúc nham - 題抱腹岩</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Tr%C3%A3i/author-NlHfXoUXzue8FcsdIodRLQ">Nguyễn Trãi</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%E1%BB%8Bnh-Ho%C3%A0i-%C4%90%E1%BB%A9c/%C4%90i%E1%BB%87u-Ph%E1%BA%A1m-Chung-C%C6%A1/poem-rj-0W0-ZZy63As-3_0VmJQ">Điệu Phạm Chung Cơ - 悼范鍾姬</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%E1%BB%8Bnh-Ho%C3%A0i-%C4%90%E1%BB%A9c/author-il2-xU_Q-nIFla-ypApHCA">Trịnh Hoài Đức</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Cao-B%C3%A1-Qu%C3%A1t/%C4%90%E1%BB%93ng-ch%C6%B0-h%E1%BB%AFu-%C4%91%C4%83ng-Tr%E1%BA%A5n-V%C5%A9-t%E1%BB%B1-chung-l%C3%A2u/poem-bYV2mTeyFo-GBUUCFryjyg">Đồng chư hữu đăng Trấn Vũ tự chung lâu - 同諸友登鎮武寺鐘樓</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Cao-B%C3%A1-Qu%C3%A1t/author-2eyz08Vw3mwjAHFJik43sA">Cao Bá Quát</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Chu-B%E1%BA%ADt/Ho%C3%A0ng-H%E1%BA%A1c-l%C3%A2u-ca/poem-U1N1CG0n1uI8WZGeNVgZfQ">Hoàng Hạc lâu ca - 黃鶴樓歌</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Chu-B%E1%BA%ADt/author-tc3-th-w6JinpHECHtJs8w">Chu Bật</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/Khi%E1%BB%83n-mu%E1%BB%99n-tr%C3%ACnh-Nghi%C3%AAm-c%C3%B4ng-nh%E1%BB%8B-th%E1%BA%ADp-v%E1%BA%ADn/poem-dMP3fYuSp4yQpHuU4-92ow">Khiển muộn trình Nghiêm công nhị thập vận - 遣悶奉呈嚴公二十韻</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%BD-Tu%E1%BA%A5n-D%C3%A2n/Lo%E1%BA%A1n-h%E1%BA%ADu-k%C3%BD-huynh/poem-wZwF15gVGWYY6RZaIZQMTQ">Loạn hậu ký huynh - 亂後寄兄</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%BD-Tu%E1%BA%A5n-D%C3%A2n/author-teRlrORlmUZ44RsTFkaMDw">Lý Tuấn Dân</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/T%C3%A2n-Kh%C3%AD-T%E1%BA%ADt/Thu%E1%BB%B7-%C4%91i%E1%BB%87u-ca-%C4%91%E1%BA%A7u-Minh-%C3%A2u/poem-WlcrTsqqVcOiF32NrBuFLA">Thuỷ điệu ca đầu - Minh âu - 水調歌頭－盟鷗</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/T%C3%A2n-Kh%C3%AD-T%E1%BA%ADt/author-cR0yq4BrF6xGIKZCvJGLSA">Tân Khí Tật</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/T%C3%ACnh-k%E1%BB%B3-2/poem-Z3HAXHa5xFTZd2w2iA2D4Q">Tình kỳ 2 - 晴其二</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/T%C3%B4-Th%E1%BB%A9c/T%C3%BAc-Ch%C3%A2u-th%E1%BB%A9-v%E1%BA%ADn-L%C6%B0u-Kinh/poem-XEw1dA_3c6paGLTgzUPpYg">Túc Châu thứ vận Lưu Kinh - 宿州次韻劉涇</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/T%C3%B4-Th%E1%BB%A9c/author-ZsPeAEZWTH-jxxg2cYfLgg">Tô Thức</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/T%C3%BAc-giang-bi%C3%AAn-c%C3%A1c/poem-rFdXJUlMe3tcUSBVjGC75g">Túc giang biên các - 宿江邊閣</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br></div>	</div>
